[SN]TITLE[SN]
Daily Politics soapbox: How to heal EU vote divisions

[SN]FIRST-SENTENCE[SN]
We are used to stark divisions in politics: Labour and Conservative, left-wing and right-wing.

[SN]RESTBODY[SN]
27 March 2017 Last updated at 13:37 BST
But with electoral upsets such as Brexit exposing fundamental divides in how people view themselves, is it time for a new way of thinking?
The writer David Goodhart thinks he has found the answer and gets on his soapbox for the Daily Politics.
